| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1617 — Recovery Inhibition (hunters)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 84cc8490-c388-52c2-9529-7a5ec8fd16b9"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
